        Data Scientist/Technical Product Manager - Consumer Data Management role will lead and directly manage key parts of the Consumer Data Platform product vision, development and execution. This role will play a critical role in advancing our personalization initiatives through development of a user360 view, implicit personalization capabilities and data visualization tools. In addition, the role will also be responsible to evangelize the technical platform and data assets across the company to achieve buy into the platform and help make it central to all Consumer related data needs. This product role is part of the Data Platforms team in the Technology organization in ESPN.
